snippet.title: Star Wars Battlefront | Official Trailer | E3 2014
snippet.description: STAR WARS™ Battlefront™ is the ultimate Star Wars battle experience, brought to life by the creators of Battlefield. Fight in epic Star Wars battles on iconic planets and rise through the ranks playing as the heroic Rebellion or the evil galactic Empire. http://bit.ly/1mzg2ZW
